
Requirements: Before running this code, ensure that the following libraries are installed:
        transformers
        torch
        pandas
        scikit-learn
        matplotlib

To install these dependencies, you can use the following command:
        pip install transformers torch pandas scikit-learn matplotlib

Dataset
        The dataset used is WIKIHOW.csv. It must contain at least two columns:

        Sentences: The text data to classify.
        Type: Whether instruction or not.
        Ensure that the CSV file is correctly encoded (latin-1 is used in the script).

Running the Program
        1. Ensure your WIKIHOW.csv file is in the same directory as the script.
        2. Run the Python script.
            python multi.py